WEBVTT

00:00.367 --> 00:03.767
The greatest guru that we have

00:04.100 --> 00:08.467
is love.

00:08.634 --> 00:11.701
Sahaj love.

00:38.033 --> 00:41.634
My father used to ask me : what do you dream?

00:41.801 --> 00:47.734
I said I want to meet all the seekers of the world,

00:48.067 --> 00:52.200
that’s what I want, all over the world, all the nations.”

02:36.767 --> 02:41.634
This is the blessing of your own seeking.

02:57.334 --> 03:02.501
Now the time has come for all of you to become Divine.

03:12.801 --> 03:15.000
Enjoy yourself,

03:15.167 --> 03:18.267
make others enjoy you.

04:00.334 --> 04:07.234
Jai Mangal Murti

06:10.300 --> 06:14.467
You are all going to be very good children, alright?

06:16.067 --> 06:19.334
Girl: "I want a kiss for my birthday, for my birthday."

06:19.501 --> 06:23.734
Today? Oh! Many happy returns of the day.

06:25.601 --> 06:28.601
Now let everyone coming for kisses alright?

06:28.767 --> 06:33.067
Come. Now all those who had kiss, should go back.

06:43.501 --> 06:46.334
Watch your parents, alright?

06:46.501 --> 06:49.634
Paolo is coming now.

06:51.067 --> 06:55.367
He kissed me, you all kissed me, alright?

06:55.667 --> 06:58.133
This one didn’t ? Alright.

06:58.300 --> 07:03.434
Thank you, thank you very much, may God bless you all.

07:06.467 --> 07:13.734
Now, we are facing little children.

07:14.367 --> 07:22.033
They are the ones who are incarnations.

07:23.801 --> 07:29.725
They are the ones who are going to lead humanity

07:29.926 --> 07:38.500
into some great advancement.

07:39.067 --> 07:43.033
The humanity has to be looked after.
